---
import "@/styles/global.css"

import { Image } from "astro:assets"
import Logo from "public/logo.png"

import DefaultLayout from "@/layouts/DefaultLayout.astro"

---

<DefaultLayout>
	<div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-start w-full  mb-10">
		<div class="h-72 flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
			<Image src={Logo} alt="Astro Logo" width={120} height={120} class="rounded-full shadow-md shadow-stone-500" />
			<h1 class="mt-2 font-medium">ATeals</h1>
		</div>

		<p class="mb-10">
			코드를 즐기며, 커피를 좋아합니다. <br />
			글 읽는 것을 좋아합니다. 글을 수집하는 것에서 멈추지 않고 작성하려 합니다. 
		</p>
		
		<p>
			<a href="/blog">Check out our blog ➡️</a>
		</p>
	</div>

	<p>
		👋 Hi, I'm ATeals. I'm a software engineer and I love building things with code. I'm also a coffee lover and I enjoy reading and writing.
	</p>
	
</DefaultLayout>